name: हिरण्यगर्भ
description: Hiraṇyagarbha is the cosmic egg in the Upanishads.  The golden womb or golden egg.  Live action 4K videoloop by mexican videoartist Rodrigo Courtney. Original music by NYC free jazzist Stan Zenkov. Starring Hanna-Katarina holding a primordial egg. Shot on location in Cofradía de Suchitlán, México. Why I keep hodling an zstranggee OBJKT?
